flowchart LR
    Cust([Customer])
    Rest([Restaurant App])

    OrderSvc[Order Service<br/>:8001]
    ResMgr[Restaurant Manager<br/>:8000]
    RouteSvc[Route Service<br/>:8003]

    T1((order-created))
    T2((res-available))
    T3((Order-placed))

    ResDB[(Postgres)]
    OrderMem[(In-memory)]
    RouteMem[(In-memory)]
    ORS([ORS API])

    Cust -->|POST /Order| OrderSvc
    OrderSvc -->|lookup lat/long| ResMgr
    OrderSvc --> T1 --> ResMgr

    ResMgr <-->|WS accept/confirm| Rest
    ResMgr --> T2 --> OrderSvc

    OrderSvc --> T3
    T3 --> ResMgr
    T3 --> RouteSvc

    RouteSvc -->|routes| ORS
    OrderSvc -.->|WS status| Cust

    ResMgr --- ResDB
    OrderSvc --- OrderMem
    RouteSvc --- RouteMem
